rbm-rpm(1)
==========

NAME
----
rbm-rpm - Build an rpm package


SYNOPSIS
--------
[verse]
'rbm rpm' <project> [options]

DESCRIPTION
-----------

Build an rpm package for the selected project.

This is equivalent to running 'rbm build --step rpm <project>'.

